rovider()` / `Security.insertProviderAt(...)` before requesting JCA/JSSE services. Preserve the existing test/native-image JVM opens for Java 9+ internals: `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED`, `--add-opens=java.base/java.net=ALL-UNNAMED`, and `--add-opens=java.base/sun.nio.ch=ALL-UNNAMED`.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The uber artifact already embeds native libraries under `META-INF/native`; failures are more likely reachability/JNI/resource metadata issues than missing dependencies.\",\n    \"Tests that exercise real sockets or SSLEngine paths may require loopback networking but not an external Docker service.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a328b3b0c999631016a42e337b6ac81909a5307d330452f9e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 5693, "output": 770, "cacheRead": 23040, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29503, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782768426594, "responseId": "resp_0a328b3b0c999631016a42e32b260c8190a356b51d2409bfbe"}}
